Package model

Contains classes that contain the logic of the program, also a middle point for accessing the database
  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    BusinessFacade
    Class tasked with managing the access to the business logic, also manages DAO access
    MIDIFactory
    Class tasked with reading .mid files and turning them into Song objects with SongNotes
    NotePlayer
    Class tasked with triggering a note or playing a whole song, should be started to play the song
    WebScrapping
    Class charged with scrapping the website and downloading the .mid files
